<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>预计本周我市有两次降水天气过程，</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>分别在周初和周末，</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>其它时段我市天气以云系变化为主。</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>大家出行要时刻注意天气变化哦！ </span></strong></span></p>
